## Notes

- See: [INDEX.md §8 — Session End & Recap](INDEX.md)
- Log parsing strips system prompt and `<details>` blocks before feeding to recap LLM
- Emergency close (DELETE) is the "discard" path; End Session (POST /end) is the "save" path
